longBusinessSummary: Standard Glass Lining Technology Limited operates as an engineering equipment manufacturer for pharmaceutical and chemical sectors in India and internationally. The company provides turnkey automated equipment solutions, such as vacuum distillation, solvent recovery, and gas dispersion. Its product portfolio consists of reaction systems; storage, separation, and drying systems; and plant, engineering, and service solutions. The company serves a range of end-use industries, such as pharmaceutical, agrochemicals, speciality and fine chemicals, active pharmaceutical ingredients, and food and bulk chemicals. Standard Glass Lining Technology Limited was incorporated in 2012 and is based in Hyderabad, India.
